data.description: Beautiful, Immaculate home featuring 2 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, Living, Florida and Dining Rooms.  Plus, it has a laundry room that is big enough for an office, craft room or whatever you fancy.  Enjoy Florida living in your tiled lanai that overlooks Lake Acacia Il. This home also has a screened in tiled front porch added in 2022.  The roof was replaced in 2015, installation of hurricane windows in 2021, A/C system in 2018, Water heater in 2022, Rain gutters 2022, new Outside paint & landscape curbing in 2022. Plumbing and electrical panels are up to date.  Home also includes an owned water softener.  The Florida Room can be closed to convert it to a 3rd bedroom. Conveniently located to the Community Amenities, grocery, banks, churches and other much needed businesses that can be reached by golf cart. Sun City Center is a premier 55 and over community which includes a fitness center, indoor and outdoor swimming pools, pickleball courts, softball, golf, tennis and many other sports activities.  Stay as busy as you like participating in the 100 + clubs the community has to offer. Tampa, Sarasota & Orlando airports are easily accessible. The Tampa Bay area is host to Buccaneer football, Lightning hockey, soccer, and baseball teams' winter here.
